# Tailwind CSS Styling Guide

## Design System

The website uses a modern, professional design system with:
- **Primary Colors**: Orange (#FF750F) and dark red (#4B0600) accents
- **Background**: Light and dark mode support
- **Typography**: Clean, modern sans-serif fonts
- **Spacing**: Consistent spacing scale

## Common Patterns

### Hero Sections
```blade
<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
        <!-- Content -->
    </div>
</div>
```

### Card Components
```blade
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
    <!-- Card content -->
</div>
```

### Gradient Text
```blade
<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
    AI-Driven Solutions
</span>
```

## Responsive Design

- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints: sm, md, lg, xl, 2xl
- Grid layouts using Tailwind's grid system
